			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Go to the lower floor of the Colony, find the Memory Library (approx. 670; -44; -10) and interact with \"S_COL_MemLib_Manuscript_002\".\r\n\r\nFor tadpoled companions (most of them), this Arcana Check happens after reading one of the illithid manuscripts.\r\n\r\nNon-tadpoled companions (Jaheira or Halsin) will have the Arcana Check upon interacting with the manuscripts, but are not able to read them. They will see the same dialog from the Arcana Check result every time they try to read it again.\r\n\r\nThe tadpoled and non-tadpoled Arcana Checks are technically two distinct checks, so the results of the checks do not cross over between those different groups of companions."
				},
				"defaultAttitudes": [
					{
						"data": [
